1. http://courses.cs.washington.edu/courses/cse552/07sp/ good material to study distributed system.
2.Have read <<J. Ousterhout, The Role of Distributed State, 1991.>>  
  "distributed state", stateful vs stateless. Both have advantages and disadvantages.
  distributed system introduces: 
  a. consistency problems,
  b. crash sensitivity,
  c. time and space overheads,
  d. complexity.
